metadata.name: #3 Elon Musk
metadata.description:
Meme inspired by Elon Musk's tweet from 24 October 2022, and his famous appearance on the TIME magazine's 29 April 2013 cover. The tweet is "dialectic" (in Greek), which refers to a discourse between people who hold different points of view about a subject but wish to establish the truth through reasoned argumentation. 

Date: 11 December 2022.
